          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2"><p align="center">Planetary American Literature: Jonathan Franzen and  Dave Eggers
          <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue5/paul_giles/bio.php" class="link3">Paul Giles</a></span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td><img src="/images/spacer.gif" width="1" height="23" border="0" alt=""></td>
